#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Objects</quote> area, where you select objects to place on your "
"playground."
msgstr ""
"A jobb oldali <quote>Tárgyak</quote> részre - itt lehet kiválasztani a "
"krumplira ráaggatni kívánt objektumot."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An actual look of the application screen may change depending on a "
"<quote>playground</quote> selected."
msgstr ""

